Revision history for Data-Format-Pretty-HTML

0.08     2013-05-16 (SHARYANTO)

         - Turn off Data::Format::Pretty::Console's autodetection of terminal
           width to format list in multiple columns.


0.07     2013-05-04 (SHARYANTO)

         - No functional changes. Adjust to Data::Format::Pretty::Console 0.24.


0.06     2013-03-17 (SHARYANTO)

         - No functional changes. Fix bug [RT#83989] (broken by
           Data::Format::Pretty::Console 0.21). Thanks, Andreas.


0.05     2012-08-07 (SHARYANTO)

         - No functional changes. Remove circular dependency on
           Data::Format::Pretty [RT#78781]. Thanks, MITHALDU.


0.04     2012-03-29 (SHARYANTO)

         - Add content_type().


0.03     2011-07-28 (SHARYANTO)

         [ENHANCEMENTS]

         - Update to Data::Format::Pretty::Console 0.10 (no header rows for
           array, hash, aoa).


0.02     2011-06-15 (SHARYANTO)

         [BUG FIXES]

         - Fix formatting for 'hot'.


0.01     2011-06-15 (SHARYANTO)

         - First release.
